_sText:
- Many challenging traps, however many of these are already used in many maps. My idea was to remake them and make the more funny and challenging.
- Every new round is playing different song out of 6.
- Custom textures and models.
- Custom 3D Skybox.
- No exploits / bugs. (If you find one Pm me)
- 3 Finishing rewards
  - Points
  - Gravity (applies in sewer level and its disabled for some places)
  - Speed


- Walkthrough: Thanks to [WeezyNL](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GLHUWP4O_tw "WeezyNL")
